  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in Edimax EW-7438RPn 1.12. This issue affects the function formEZCHNwlanSetup of the file /goform/formEZCHNwlanSetu of the component POST Request Handler. Performing a manipulation of the argument method results in command injection. Remote exploitation of the attack is possible. The exploit is now public and may be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
